      "text": [
        " كَانَ يَقُولُ : «اِصْحَبْ مَنْ تَتَزَيَّنُ بِهِ وَ لاَ تَصْحَبْ مَنْ يَتَزَيَّنُ بِكَ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2440 - Ishaq ibn Jarir narrated from Abu Abdullah (as), who said:\n\"Accompany those who add to your virtue, and do not accompany those who seek to gain virtue from you.\""
        ]
      }
